WEBVTT

00:01.410 --> 00:05.460
We've got our contact set up you've got about six like I've got are 600.

00:05.460 --> 00:12.030
Does it matter the time might come that you might need to give someone access to your contacts.

00:12.430 --> 00:13.530
Well you're in a group.

00:13.860 --> 00:19.590
And one of the exec's requests say for example access to your contacts so he can kind of watch the whole

00:19.590 --> 00:20.640
discussion.

00:20.640 --> 00:22.800
There are a lot of reasons why you might want to do this.

00:22.830 --> 00:24.860
I want to give access to my wife.

00:25.070 --> 00:25.560
Why.

00:25.650 --> 00:26.210
I don't know.

00:26.220 --> 00:26.920
She's my wife.

00:26.940 --> 00:28.830
But she's also my business partner.

00:28.980 --> 00:32.570
And so well she needs access and so I'm going to give her access.

00:32.640 --> 00:33.490
How do I do that.

00:33.630 --> 00:39.140
Well number one she does have to have a Google account with real and it has to be that.

00:39.330 --> 00:43.960
So let's go up to the word more and go down to manage delegation's settings.

00:44.870 --> 00:47.990
Come down into invite people and begin typing.

00:47.990 --> 00:53.010
In my case Bonnie now she has several domains and accounts.

00:53.030 --> 00:54.690
This is the one I want.

00:54.800 --> 00:57.110
You can add a message which I want to do.

00:57.110 --> 00:59.800
Bonnie dearest love of my life.

01:00.530 --> 01:03.270
Here are my contacts.

01:03.290 --> 01:05.060
Treat them with care.

01:05.120 --> 01:06.820
I'm going to send one to myself.

01:06.830 --> 01:07.300
Why.

01:07.370 --> 01:10.370
Well it gives me a record so I know.

01:10.370 --> 01:11.480
Click send.

01:11.630 --> 01:13.370
And there it goes.

01:13.370 --> 01:15.670
She can now edit like done.

01:15.920 --> 01:18.010
And she now has access now.

01:18.050 --> 01:25.520
Any time I want to I can come back into more and go into managed delegation settings and click here

01:25.760 --> 01:26.840
and remove those.

01:27.110 --> 01:30.260
You'll have to come down here and say save changes.

01:30.470 --> 01:31.340
Click done.

01:31.340 --> 01:33.730
And now she doesn't have access anymore.

01:33.740 --> 01:37.910
There are times when you want to give people access to your contacts.

01:38.000 --> 01:38.800
That's how you do it.
